{{Infobox journal | title = Plant Pathology | discipline = [[Phytopathology]] | abbreviation = Plant Pathol. | cover = Plantpathologyjournal.gif | editor = [[Matt Dickinson (plant pathologist)|Matt Dickinson]] | publisher = [[Wiley-Blackwell]] on behalf of the [[British Society for Plant Pathology]] | country = | history = 1952-present | frequency = Bimonthly | impact = 2.125 | impact-year = 2011 | website = http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/journal.asp?ref=0032-0862 | OCLC = | ISSN = 0032-0862 }} '''''Plant Pathology''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] published by [[Wiley-Blackwell]] in association with the [[British Society for Plant Pathology]]. It was established in 1952 and was originally published by the Ministry of Agriculture. The journal publishes research articles and critical reviews on all aspects of plant pathology except for articles on pesticide and resistance screening.<ref>{{cite web |author=S. J. Roberts |url=http://www.bspp.org.uk |title=British Society for Plant Pathology - Home Page |publisher=Bspp.org.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-03-05}}</ref> The [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Matt Dickinson (plant pathologist)|Matt Dickinson]].
